## Bard Prompts 

    # Summerize the news  
        Summarize current events in banking in the US in simple words and in list form. Makes a small conclusion with the risks.

    # Search for academic references
        Makes a table with the best books that talk about the reconstruction of Europe after WW2 (title, date, author, short summary).\

    # Find the best places
        I'm visiting Austin, Texas next week. Name 5 lesser-known places that I absolutely must see.

    # Conduct data analysis
        Give me the evolution of computer sales in the US since 2017 in a table and interpret the results.

    # Get new ideas
        Look at the news around rumors of upcoming Apple products and give me ideas for blog posts.

    # 
